Market Analysis and Size

The clinical information technology (IT) market is fuelled by increased R&D spending in the sector by biotech and pharmaceutical companies, resulting in adopting technologies that provide cost-effective solutions. The growing need for better data standardization is driving market growth. The increased number of clinical trials, particularly in emerging Asia Pacific countries, is creating opportunities for the market growth of clinical information technology solutions. This is expected to be boosted further by pharmaceutical companies' adoption of EDC systems.

